### 9️⃣ تعديل الـ Hooks

**النمط العام لكل hook:**
```javascript
// ====== قبل: ======
const itemsRef = collection(db, "inventory_items");

// ====== بعد: ======
import { useTenant } from "../context/TenantContext";

const { tenantId } = useTenant();
const itemsRef = collection(db, `tenants/${tenantId}/inventory_items`);
```

**القائمة الكاملة:**
| Hook | الـ collection اللي يتغير |
|------|--------------------------|
| `useInventory.js` | `inventory_items` → `tenants/${tenantId}/inventory_items` |
| `useTransactions.js` | `transactions` → `tenants/${tenantId}/transactions` |
| `useCategories.js` | `categories` → `tenants/${tenantId}/categories` |
| `useTradeNames.js` | `trade_names` → `tenants/${tenantId}/trade_names` |
| `useAlerts.js` | `alerts` → `tenants/${tenantId}/alerts` |
| `useAlertSync.js` | `alerts` → `tenants/${tenantId}/alerts` |
| `useBatches.js` | `inventory_items/{id}/batches` → `tenants/${tenantId}/inventory_items/{id}/batches` |
| `useQuickDispense.js` | يستخدم inventory + transactions → نفس التعديل |
| `useRestockScan.js` | يستخدم inventory + transactions → نفس التعديل |

